WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.389
Hey, good morning, family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:04.910
be with you all again today. First off, I

00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:06.829
just want to tell you thank you for all

00:00:06.839 --> 00:00:10.190
the likes and all the subscribes; it is a

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:12.470
blessing to us.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:15.470
I believe I'm right at 74,000

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:18.189
people, and we got two people born

00:00:18.199 --> 00:00:21.109
again with this last video from what

00:00:21.119 --> 00:00:23.509
I know; they told us in an

00:00:23.519 --> 00:00:25.390
email. I just want to

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:28.230
tell you all thank you for all of the

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:31.189
support you're giving us;

00:00:31.199 --> 00:00:33.229
it is a true blessing. We're getting

00:00:33.239 --> 00:00:36.229
the gospel out, and it is reaching the

00:00:36.239 --> 00:00:38.910
lost throughout the whole world. People

00:00:38.920 --> 00:00:41.270
commenting in the comment section

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:42.910
helps us, and I just want to tell you

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:47.350
thank you. So, here we are at

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:50.350
the end of October, and I told you all

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:53.750
to be watching Gavin, and he decides to

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:57.790
make a trip to China for five days to

00:00:57.800 --> 00:00:59.950
try to do some kind of ambassador

00:00:59.950 --> 00:00:59.960
thing

00:00:59.960 --> 00:01:02.110
for the Green New Deal. Basically, the bottom

00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:04.710
line is he's campaigning. I'm telling

00:01:04.720 --> 00:01:06.590
you, I believe the man's going to

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:08.670
announce he's going to be running

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:10.510
for president, vice president, or

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:12.630
whatever for the Democratic party. I just

00:01:12.640 --> 00:01:14.469
believe there's something to this. I've

00:01:14.479 --> 00:01:17.109
seen him in a vision several times. Maybe it

00:01:17.119 --> 00:01:18.950
won't be this time; maybe it will be this

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:21.310
time. We will see, but I believe we will

00:01:21.320 --> 00:01:23.670
see something soon. He

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:28.310
was in China doing a lot of

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:30.270
photo ops, and it looked like he was

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:33.109
campaigning to me. We'll see;

00:01:33.119 --> 00:01:35.510
watch Michelle, and if Michelle comes

00:01:35.520 --> 00:01:36.950
out and does something, I believe they

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:40.670
will run together.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:43.149
Let's just keep watching. I

00:01:43.159 --> 00:01:45.950
was praying about what I

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:47.789
should talk to you all about today,

00:01:47.799 --> 00:01:49.429
and the Lord told me he

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:51.310
wanted me to talk to you all about the

00:01:51.320 --> 00:01:53.630
angels again. I said, 'Well, Lord,

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:55.670
they've already heard that,'and he said,

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:58.310
'Brandon, how many times have you heard a

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:00.749
word over and over again and

00:02:00.759 --> 00:02:03.709
you still don't get it?'He said faith

00:02:03.719 --> 00:02:06.550
comes by hearing and hearing by the word

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:09.550
of God. He said, 'Son, there's a lot

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:11.190
of times you've heard sermons

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.750
over and over again, some of my

00:02:12.760 --> 00:02:14.309
favorite ones, and you still

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:16.589
don't have the full manifestation on

00:02:16.589 --> 00:02:16.599
it.'He

00:02:16.599 --> 00:02:19.550
said it's going to be repetitive when

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:23.150
it becomes a rhema word for their life. Rhema

00:02:23.150 --> 00:02:23.160
words—he

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:25.910
said that's what it takes.

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:28.430
Faith comes by hearing and hearing.

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:30.990
It didn't say

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:32.550
you have to hear it just once;

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:35.270
it comes by

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:36.949
hearing the word of God over and over

00:02:36.959 --> 00:02:39.350
again. So I want to say this to

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:42.470
you all about today: the Lord said

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:45.790
to me

00:02:45.790 --> 00:02:45.800
that

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:47.910
in these last seconds

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:50.589
of the last days, there is going to be

00:02:50.599 --> 00:02:53.070
divine

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:56.270
manifestations of angelic

00:02:56.280 --> 00:03:01.149
encounters for protection, for

00:03:01.159 --> 00:03:03.830
visitations, and manifestations of the

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:06.589
glory of God. I'm going to tell

00:03:06.599 --> 00:03:09.830
you about one of these manifestations

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:12.990
that we had as a family coming home

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:16.869
from work one day. My wife and I

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:18.589
worked at the church

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:21.949
for years, and I

00:03:21.949 --> 00:03:21.959
cleaned

00:03:21.959 --> 00:03:23.710
the rugs there. I cleaned the carpets, the

00:03:23.720 --> 00:03:25.869
floors, and everything. It was a

00:03:25.879 --> 00:03:27.830
Saturday afternoon

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:29.830
in

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.869
the middle of the summer, really

00:03:31.879 --> 00:03:35.910
hot outside. My wife was

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:38.270
pregnant at the time with our daughter.

00:03:38.280 --> 00:03:41.070
We're driving home in my truck,

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:43.550
and the gas gauge

00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:47.190
was broken, so you never knew

00:03:47.200 --> 00:03:49.990
how much gas you had;

00:03:49.990 --> 00:03:50.000
you'd

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.869
just be guessing.

00:03:51.879 --> 00:03:53.990
It was a long drive.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:55.429
I

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:57.589
thought I had enough. We're driving

00:03:57.599 --> 00:04:00.750
home, and all of a sudden, the engine

00:04:00.760 --> 00:04:03.830
turns off. My wife

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:05.949
said, 'Oh honey, what's

00:04:07.799 --> 00:04:09.429
wrong?'I

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:12.949
pulled over, and I

00:04:12.959 --> 00:04:15.069
was freaking out

00:04:15.079 --> 00:04:17.629
because it's hot outside and I

00:04:17.639 --> 00:04:19.469
had my pregnant wife in the car and my

00:04:19.479 --> 00:04:22.830
two children: my

00:04:22.840 --> 00:04:25.070
son, who's doing the filming right now,

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:26.870
and my oldest daughter, who had

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:30.430
special needs. I said, 'Oh

00:04:30.440 --> 00:04:32.469
no, I believe we just ran out of

00:04:32.479 --> 00:04:34.950
gas.'I

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:36.430
just started praying in the Holy Ghost,

00:04:36.440 --> 00:04:38.230
and I grabbed the wheel

00:04:38.230 --> 00:04:38.240
and

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:40.110
said, 'God, we need a miracle right

00:04:40.110 --> 00:04:40.120
now,'because

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:42.310
it was a long way to the gas station.

00:04:48.840 --> 00:04:51.390
It was

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:54.830
probably 105 degrees at least.

00:04:57.919 --> 00:04:59.990
In the truck, it was really hot.

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:06.070
I said, 'Lord,

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:07.870
I don't want to get out of the truck

00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:11.950
to walk to the gas station several

00:05:11.950 --> 00:05:11.960
miles.'We're

00:05:11.960 --> 00:05:14.469
all just

00:05:14.479 --> 00:05:16.629
praying in the

00:05:16.639 --> 00:05:17.830
spirit.

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:20.189
All of a sudden, I

00:05:20.199 --> 00:05:23.629
feel a bang

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:25.590
on the back of our tailgate.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:29.590
I thought somebody from the

00:05:29.600 --> 00:05:32.070
highway just had rear-ended us.

00:05:34.319 --> 00:05:37.230
It was that much of a jolt.

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:41.230
But

00:05:41.240 --> 00:05:45.309
it wasn't violent; it was just a

00:05:45.319 --> 00:05:48.870
nudge. All of a sudden, I see this

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:53.189
massive angel with these wings out,

00:05:53.199 --> 00:05:56.510
humongous, spread out

00:05:56.520 --> 00:05:59.749
over like this, and he smiles real big at

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:02.870
me. I screamed because it startled me.

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:05.070
He

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:09.589
was

00:06:09.599 --> 00:06:12.150
full of joy; his whole face was

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:14.629
radiating from the glory of God.

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:19.469
I'm seeing it in

00:06:19.479 --> 00:06:22.430
the spirit, in the supernatural, through

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:25.309
a vision. He grabs

00:06:25.309 --> 00:06:25.319
ahold

00:06:25.319 --> 00:06:28.230
of our tailgate

00:06:28.230 --> 00:06:28.240
and

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:30.950
starts pushing us down the

00:06:30.960 --> 00:06:34.189
highway. All of a sudden, we start

00:06:34.199 --> 00:06:37.430
gaining speed,

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:39.029
going faster and faster. I

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:42.670
turned my blinker on and I

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:44.749
entered

00:06:44.759 --> 00:06:47.309
onto

00:06:47.319 --> 00:06:49.029
the

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:51.390
highway. We're going about 65 miles an

00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:54.469
hour, then we start going to

00:06:54.479 --> 00:06:58.710
70 with the engine off.

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:01.670
We start picking

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:03.510
up speed

00:07:03.510 --> 00:07:03.520
and

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:06.309
passing people in the

00:07:06.309 --> 00:07:06.319
left-hand

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:09.230
lane

00:07:09.240 --> 00:07:12.110
with the angel pushing us.

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:23.990
We go two and a half

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:26.150
miles

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:30.270
all the way

00:07:30.280 --> 00:07:32.869
to where we exit off the

00:07:32.879 --> 00:07:35.230
highway. We go down

00:07:35.240 --> 00:07:39.270
the ramp to

00:07:39.270 --> 00:07:39.280
a stoplight,

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:43.070
completely stop,

00:07:43.080 --> 00:07:46.790
then turn right, go another quarter of

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:49.230
a mile, and turn

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:51.270
into the gas

00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:54.029
station. The angel, right before we

00:07:54.039 --> 00:07:57.309
get to the pump, yanks on the back of the

00:07:57.319 --> 00:08:00.350
tailgate and stops us right in front of

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:03.309
the pump. We all just started screaming

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:04.990
and worshiping.

00:08:12.599 --> 00:08:16.149
It was so

00:08:16.159 --> 00:08:18.909
overwhelming. My wife and I, and my

00:08:21.990 --> 00:08:22.000
kids—my

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:27.469
son

00:08:29.599 --> 00:08:31.309
could sense

00:08:31.319 --> 00:08:33.230
that the car was moving.

00:08:38.120 --> 00:08:40.829
We all just started

00:08:40.829 --> 00:08:40.839
praising

00:08:40.839 --> 00:08:42.949
the Lord, and

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:45.310
everybody else at the gas station

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:48.150
was looking at us like,

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:50.430
'What are they yelling about?'But we were

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:52.150
yelling because the windows were down

00:08:52.150 --> 00:08:52.160
and

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:53.829
the truck

00:08:53.839 --> 00:08:55.990
was off,

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:58.590
and

00:08:58.600 --> 00:08:59.870
we

00:08:59.880 --> 00:09:02.430
were

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.069
praising

00:09:04.079 --> 00:09:06.150
the Lord.

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:09.150
God

00:09:09.160 --> 00:09:11.550
supernaturally sent an

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:14.949
angel to protect my wife and children on

00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:17.630
the side of a highway.

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:19.710
He knew that it was

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:21.750
dangerous for my pregnant wife

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.910
and

00:09:23.920 --> 00:09:25.829
my other children to be

00:09:25.839 --> 00:09:27.590
there.

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:32.030
God came through, and

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:34.670
he'll do the same for you. It's

00:09:34.680 --> 00:09:36.829
time to believe for the miraculous in

00:09:36.839 --> 00:09:40.470
your life. Nothing's too big for God.

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:47.230
He wants all things to

00:09:47.230 --> 00:09:47.240
be

00:09:47.240 --> 00:09:49.870
possible to him that will

00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:52.949
believe. There are so many times

00:09:52.959 --> 00:09:55.829
that Jesus has come through

00:09:55.839 --> 00:09:58.389
supernaturally for us, and this is just

00:09:58.399 --> 00:10:00.550
one of the testimonies that stood

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:03.430
out to me the most.

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.430
People always ask me,

00:10:08.440 --> 00:10:11.509
'How do you hear the Lord the way you

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:15.829
do?'I'm

00:10:17.839 --> 00:10:20.829
not anything special; I just

00:10:20.839 --> 00:10:22.190
pray and I

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:25.350
obey. I'm hungry for his voice

00:10:25.350 --> 00:10:25.360
and

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:27.910
his presence, and I

00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:30.670
seek him.

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:55.910
I really believe with all my heart

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:57.310
this is what it comes down to:

00:10:57.320 --> 00:11:00.310
do something

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:03.550
that you don't like doing and do it with

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:06.750
all your heart. Whether that's

00:11:06.760 --> 00:11:09.750
cleaning for the nursery

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:13.190
or

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:16.750
things of service

00:11:16.760 --> 00:11:19.910
towards a widow,

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:21.230
like when I mow my

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:23.750
grandmother's yard. It isn't what

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:24.990
your flesh wants to do in the middle of

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:26.949
the summer, but I

00:11:26.959 --> 00:11:28.269
ride

00:11:28.279 --> 00:11:30.550
around her

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:35.230
acre of land—she's 88 years

00:11:35.230 --> 00:11:35.240
old—as

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:38.629
an act of love.

00:11:42.920 --> 00:11:45.030
I've done

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:47.430
that for 12 years now.

00:11:47.430 --> 00:11:47.440
I

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:49.230
do it

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:51.509
for free

00:11:51.519 --> 00:11:54.030
because I love her.

00:11:54.040 --> 00:11:55.870
I realize whenever I get

00:11:55.880 --> 00:11:57.509
on that mower, or when she

00:11:57.509 --> 00:11:57.519
says,

00:11:57.519 --> 00:11:59.430
'Son, can you help me pull the weeds

00:12:02.550 --> 00:12:02.560
in

00:12:06.670 --> 00:12:06.680
my

00:12:08.639 --> 00:12:11.389
flowerbed?'that

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.750
I'm sacrificing my time.

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:24.110
I'll be out there

00:12:24.110 --> 00:12:24.120
mowing

00:12:24.120 --> 00:12:26.189
and the Lord starts talking,

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:31.230
clear as crystal.

00:12:34.199 --> 00:12:35.189
He'll talk

00:12:35.199 --> 00:12:37.230
about investments. People say, 'Oh, God

00:12:37.230 --> 00:12:37.240
doesn't

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:38.750
talk about investments.'You don't

00:12:38.760 --> 00:12:40.910
know God. I feel sorry for you because

00:12:40.910 --> 00:12:40.920
of how ignorant you are to

00:12:40.920 --> 00:12:43.150
who God really is.

00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:53.910
When you volunteer

00:12:53.920 --> 00:12:55.470
at the church

00:12:55.470 --> 00:12:55.480
and

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:58.030
do acts of service,

00:12:59.760 --> 00:13:02.990
it's a

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:07.150
brokenness where he talks to you. A

00:13:07.160 --> 00:13:10.750
wild horse is a beautiful animal,

00:13:13.720 --> 00:13:15.550
but it is not able to be

00:13:15.560 --> 00:13:18.590
used correctly until it's broken.

00:13:24.360 --> 00:13:27.750
The more the horse is broken, the

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.870
greater the service.

00:13:32.920 --> 00:13:35.389
Our lives are broken before the Lord.

00:13:35.399 --> 00:13:37.870
He's the potter, we're the clay.

00:13:42.480 --> 00:13:44.470
I worked at the

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:47.310
church for almost

00:13:47.320 --> 00:13:48.750
15

00:13:48.760 --> 00:13:51.189
years.

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:56.949
I was a janitor

00:13:56.959 --> 00:13:59.230
every single day; I cleaned

00:13:59.230 --> 00:13:59.240
and

00:13:59.240 --> 00:14:00.790
cleaned. There

00:14:00.790 --> 00:14:00.800
were

00:14:00.800 --> 00:14:03.350
times my flesh was screaming, 'I do not

00:14:03.360 --> 00:14:05.829
want to do this anymore!'and the Lord

00:14:05.829 --> 00:14:05.839
said,

00:14:05.839 --> 00:14:09.110
'Do it

00:14:12.069 --> 00:14:12.079
again.'He

00:14:14.040 --> 00:14:16.350
would just tell me to keep

00:14:16.360 --> 00:14:19.389
going.

00:14:19.399 --> 00:14:22.069
Honor

00:14:22.079 --> 00:14:23.949
the pastor.

00:14:27.959 --> 00:14:30.749
He said,

00:14:30.759 --> 00:14:33.790
'No, not only do you not touch him

00:14:33.800 --> 00:14:35.350
with your mouth, but you don't touch

00:14:35.360 --> 00:14:37.590
him in your heart.'He said, 'The willing and obedient will eat the

00:14:37.590 --> 00:14:37.600
good of the land, Brandon. You may be obedient, but

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:39.829
you're not willing.'Years go by, and finally, I started enjoying

00:14:39.829 --> 00:14:39.839
my life there and ministering to the people around

00:14:39.839 --> 00:14:41.430
me. I said, 'I'm not going to

00:14:44.720 --> 00:14:47.310
complain in my heart

00:15:16.269 --> 00:15:16.279
anymore.'It

00:15:38.160 --> 00:15:41.150
was a dying to self,

00:15:41.160 --> 00:15:44.110
continually practicing his presence,

00:15:44.120 --> 00:15:46.350
continually getting on the Potter's

00:15:46.350 --> 00:15:46.360
wheel

00:15:46.360 --> 00:15:48.629
and saying, 'Father, not my will but yours

00:15:48.639 --> 00:15:50.350
be

00:15:54.790 --> 00:15:54.800
done.'So

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:03.030
I got on that

00:16:03.040 --> 00:16:05.350
Potter's wheel and I kept walking it out.

00:16:05.350 --> 00:16:05.360
I'd

00:16:05.360 --> 00:16:06.910
go in there and

00:16:06.910 --> 00:16:06.920
they'd

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:09.230
treat me like trash, and I'd say,

00:16:09.240 --> 00:16:10.590
'I'm going to pray for them

00:16:10.600 --> 00:16:12.509
today.'People

00:16:12.519 --> 00:16:14.110
would

00:16:14.120 --> 00:16:16.309
get healed, delivered,

00:16:16.309 --> 00:16:16.319
and

00:16:16.319 --> 00:16:18.550
set free.

00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:37.790
About six years later,

00:16:39.319 --> 00:16:42.069
the Lord came to me and

00:16:42.079 --> 00:16:45.230
said, 'You're done.

00:16:45.240 --> 00:16:46.350
You

00:16:47.629 --> 00:16:47.639
passed

00:16:50.319 --> 00:16:52.790
your test. On

00:16:52.800 --> 00:16:54.829
this day, you're going to quit your job

00:17:09.799 --> 00:17:11.750
here.'God

00:17:30.240 --> 00:17:32.549
has been

00:17:32.559 --> 00:17:35.190
faithful, and out of that came this

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:37.990
YouTube channel.

00:17:44.120 --> 00:17:45.750
He wanted me to

00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:54.710
go through the refiner's

00:17:54.720 --> 00:17:57.510
fire, and that's how the voice

00:17:57.520 --> 00:17:59.830
of God was birthed out of

00:17:59.830 --> 00:17:59.840
me—through

00:17:59.840 --> 00:18:02.070
obedience in the

00:18:02.080 --> 00:18:04.350
small things.

00:18:29.039 --> 00:18:32.789
This is a

00:18:32.799 --> 00:18:34.590
time for great manifestations.

00:18:34.590 --> 00:18:34.600
It

00:18:34.600 --> 00:18:37.270
isn't a time

00:18:37.280 --> 00:18:39.630
to shrink back and get

00:18:39.640 --> 00:18:41.669
discouraged about

00:18:41.679 --> 00:18:43.950
the wars and the

00:18:43.960 --> 00:18:46.310
craziness in this world.

00:18:51.640 --> 00:18:53.390
It's time for us to show the love of

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:56.149
God to people like never before. It's

00:18:56.159 --> 00:18:58.350
time for us to be the salt of the

00:18:58.360 --> 00:19:00.909
earth.

00:19:06.679 --> 00:19:09.310
When

00:19:09.320 --> 00:19:11.510
times get hard, people are going to be

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:14.310
looking for you.

00:19:44.159 --> 00:19:47.070
You've got to keep yourself on

00:19:47.080 --> 00:19:50.029
the Potter's wheel in these last days and

00:19:50.039 --> 00:19:53.630
say, 'God, here I am, use me.

00:20:00.360 --> 00:20:03.830
Send me into the

00:20:03.840 --> 00:20:07.230
nations, the city, and

00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:10.070
the workplace, and let my

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:13.549
light shine so bright that the glory of

00:20:13.559 --> 00:20:15.750
God would be radiating out of my face

00:20:15.760 --> 00:20:19.590
like Moses.'I pray it all the time.

00:20:36.880 --> 00:20:40.789
'Lord, use me.

00:20:40.799 --> 00:20:44.350
Here am I, Lord, send

00:20:57.630 --> 00:20:57.640
me.'I

00:21:11.279 --> 00:21:13.149
don't want to do these videos by

00:21:13.159 --> 00:21:16.230
myself; if the Holy Spirit is not in this

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:19.390
video, I don't want to waste your time. It's

00:21:19.390 --> 00:21:19.400
all

00:21:19.400 --> 00:21:22.149
by

00:21:22.159 --> 00:21:25.669
the grace

00:21:25.679 --> 00:21:27.510
of God.

00:21:48.840 --> 00:21:52.430
So

00:21:52.440 --> 00:21:54.830
I pray for you all, and I believe God

00:21:54.840 --> 00:21:56.750
that something supernaturally

00:21:56.750 --> 00:21:56.760
is

00:21:56.760 --> 00:21:59.430
going to happen for you today—for your

00:21:59.440 --> 00:22:01.870
unsaved loved ones to get born again, for

00:22:01.880 --> 00:22:04.230
your deliverance, and for all the healing

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:07.310
that you need. Jesus Christ paid the

00:22:07.320 --> 00:22:10.669
price for you.

00:22:15.760 --> 00:22:19.350
He came to set the captives free,

00:22:19.360 --> 00:22:22.549
and whom the Son sets free is free

00:22:22.559 --> 00:22:26.029
indeed.

00:22:37.600 --> 00:22:40.110
Reach up right now and grab it by faith.

00:22:47.400 --> 00:22:50.950
I will lack no good thing, and I

00:22:50.960 --> 00:22:54.029
will live long and finish strong. I will

00:22:58.679 --> 00:23:02.310
be

00:23:05.600 --> 00:23:08.950
a light in the darkness.

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:24.310
Father, we just thank you

00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:26.590
in the name of Jesus for every

00:23:26.600 --> 00:23:28.590
person represented here

00:23:28.600 --> 00:23:31.549
today. We call them healed and whole.

00:23:57.640 --> 00:24:00.190
I rebuke

00:24:00.200 --> 00:24:02.070
sickness and disease off of you in the

00:24:02.080 --> 00:24:04.870
name of Jesus.

00:24:07.159 --> 00:24:08.789
From the top of your head to the

00:24:08.789 --> 00:24:08.799
soles

00:24:08.799 --> 00:24:11.950
of your feet, you are delivered from that

00:24:11.960 --> 00:24:14.149
infirmity, whether

00:24:14.159 --> 00:24:17.110
it be kidney disease, cancer,

00:24:17.120 --> 00:24:20.110
diabetes, or heart disease. I call

00:24:49.720 --> 00:24:53.750
restoration of marriages

00:24:56.510 --> 00:24:56.520
and

00:24:58.320 --> 00:25:01.190
take authority over demonic

00:25:01.200 --> 00:25:02.990
spirits causing division.

00:25:08.360 --> 00:25:11.389
I call wayward children to come home

00:25:11.399 --> 00:25:14.389
in Jesus'name.

00:25:14.389 --> 00:25:14.399
Angels

00:25:14.399 --> 00:25:16.990
of

00:25:16.990 --> 00:25:17.000
the

00:25:17.000 --> 00:25:18.950
Lord,

00:25:26.480 --> 00:25:28.549
go right now

00:25:28.559 --> 00:25:30.190
and

00:25:30.200 --> 00:25:31.510
bring

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:33.510
our children home.

00:25:37.480 --> 00:25:40.230
Satan,

00:25:42.919 --> 00:25:45.389
you will not touch our loved ones

00:25:45.399 --> 00:25:47.590
anymore. We

00:25:57.120 --> 00:25:59.470
are

00:26:10.200 --> 00:26:12.669
not beggars; we're believers.

00:26:14.360 --> 00:26:16.669
He's not

00:26:16.679 --> 00:26:18.789
moved by your need; he's moved by your

00:26:18.799 --> 00:26:22.350
faith.

00:26:31.720 --> 00:26:34.230
My Father

00:26:34.240 --> 00:26:37.029
will supply all my needs according to

00:26:37.039 --> 00:26:40.470
his riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

00:26:46.039 --> 00:26:47.630
Thank you for all the

00:26:47.640 --> 00:26:50.110
kindness you showed to my family. God

00:26:50.120 --> 00:26:52.389
bless you guys.

00:26:52.399 --> 00:26:55.310
We love you so

00:26:55.320 --> 00:26:57.909
much, and we'll see you next time. Have

00:26:57.919 --> 00:27:02.080
a blessed day. Bye-bye.

